A simple about page, in the colors of the pan pride flag.

Features:
    Custom scrollbar, tooltips, text selection and mobile toolbar.
    Responsive layout.
    Multiple sections.
    Icon navigation.

Rules:
    1) Do not edit beyond recogniton.
